      </article>

      <article class="package-card featured reveal">
        <p class="package-tier">Campaign Launch (Growth)</p>
        <p class="package-price">&#8377;89,999</p>
        <p class="package-sub">per month</p>
        <div class="package-divider"></div>
        <ul class="package-deliverables">
          <li>5 Cinematic Product Stills</li>
          <li>1 Brand Kit Layout</li>
          <li>2 Campaign Hero</li>
